(Not sure if my e-mail of Unicron leaving Rapa Nui got through)

Unicron:



The ancient robot thought for a brief moment, knowing he could go as he 
looked.  In a bright flash, his form had changed to mask his identity.  It 
wasn't much of a change.  His body had shrunk a few feet and his colors had 
changed to match the size and color of Unitron.

Hovering several feet from the EMP field, the true leader of the Brotherhood 
smiled.  He activated a comm. link and sent out a transmission.  

"This is Vehement of the Brotherhood.  I am interested in your sales."
